First and foremost, the staff at Wave Pharmacy were incredibly knowledgeable and courteous. They took the time to understand my requirements and offered personalized recommendations tailored to my needs. Their professionalism and expertise truly set them apart.

As a sportsperson, this surgery meant everything to me. I spoke to multiple doctors before making my decision, but the confidence I felt after meeting Dr. Bibek Basukala was unmatched. He explained the entire procedure in detail what would be done, which implants would be used, the pros and cons of each and that clarity made all the difference. He‚Äôs not just an excellent surgeon, but a genuinely kind, humble, and compassionate human being. I trusted him completely with my career, and I‚Äôm grateful I did. Truly one of the best in the country.

A heartfelt thank you to the nurses in the orthopedic ward, words will never be enough to express my gratitude for your care and support.

The physiotherapy team is exceptional. I came from the U.S. and have experienced sports physio there as well, and the recovery I‚Äôve had here surprised many people. Despite the huge patient load, they work with patience, care, and a constant smile. I never once felt like just another patient, more like family.

There is definitely room for improvement on the management side, hence the four stars.

A huge shoutout once again to Dr. Bibek Basukala, Rushma Dd, and the entire physiotherapy team, especially Nikki Dd.
